name: Amber Mountains
desc: The Amber Mountains are a mountain range located near the west coast of the Usean continent. They extend from the northwestern coast between Farbanti and Cape Rainy to the Gunther region. The range also includes some mountain peaks located directly north of Gunther.

name: Vladimir Mountains
desc: The Vladimir Mountains are a vast mountain range in northeastern Yuktobania, several hundred kilometers due east of Cruik Fortress.

name: Jilachi Desert
desc: The Jilachi Desert is a vast desert region located in central Yuktobania, east of Sonza and south of the city of Zakat. During the Circum-Pacific War in late 2010, the desert became the site of a widespread engagement between the Osean and Yuktobanian military.

name: Hatties Desert
desc: The Hatties Desert is a desert region located in western Usea. It is the location of the Spaceguard Turret Network.

name: Sonza
desc: Sonza is a rugged, arid region in eastern Yuktobania, northeast of Lake Lyibar and east of the Jilachi Desert.

name: Altoora Desert
desc: Altoora Desert is located in the deserted northern area of USEA, next to the east of Sandbury Desert. In 1998, it was verified by Unified Command as the location of the Usean Rebel Force's elemental particle research lab, codenamed Pancake.

name: Sandbury Desert
desc: Sandbury Desert is a vast desert located in San Salvacion, in north-central Usea, southeast of White Valley and north of the Lambert Mountains.

name: Moloch Desert
desc: The Moloch Desert is a large desert located in central Anea, northwest of Gracemeria, Emmeria. It is a dry plain with sand dunes spread throughout the area, as well as a river traveling east-west. An Emmerian air base is located south of the river.
